<p>ShopReel scrapes business data from <strong>Google Maps</strong> using <strong>SerpAPI</strong> and individual shop websites, compiling the results into a structured Excel file.</p>

<hr>

<h3>Get Your SerpAPI Key</h3>
<ul>
    <li>Go to <a href="https://serpapi.com/" target="_blank">SerpAPI</a> and create a free account.</li>
    <li>After signing up, an API key will be automatically generated for your account.</li>
    <li>Locate the section called <code>Your Private API Key</code> and copy the key for use in ShopReel.</li>
</ul>
