<h5>Output Files</h5>
<p>After running a search, ShopReel generates Excel files containing the shop data. The behavior depends on how you run the search:</p>

<ul>
    <li><strong>Manual Input:</strong>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>simple_shop_details.xlsx:</strong> Generated immediately after the SerpAPI search completes. Contains basic shop information and can be reused in subsequent runs to avoid additional API requests for the same dataset.</li>
            <li><strong>shop_details.xlsx:</strong> Includes detailed information collected from each shop‚Äôs website (emails, online store availability, social media profiles, etc.).</li>
        </ul>
    </li>
    <li><strong>File Import:</strong>
        <ul>
            <li>Only the final <strong>shop_details.xlsx</strong> file will be downloaded, since the <strong>simple_shop_details.xlsx</strong> file is already provided for reuse.</li>
        </ul>
    </li>
</ul>

